Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天還有炒面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.71,0:15:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
