Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 去那孩子那裏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就是食堂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是你的同伴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇馬 已經沒事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢適應和大家相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:50.81,shuoming,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小久和小月都吃過飯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.74,0:16:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺璃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.20,0:16:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺璃的聲音就像魔法一樣能給大家帶來幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的孫女失去聲音 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是因為精神上的原因造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心 總有一天能說話的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那首歌也一定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.74,0:17:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是首不錯的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.60,0:17:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新宿區附近出現Larva反應
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數據庫沒有相應資料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.25,0:17:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是新的個體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.09,0:17:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反應等級 藍色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.99,0:17:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.61,0:17:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然看起來不怎麼樣 但是味道很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔬菜是這裏的溫室裏培養的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然吃蔬菜是很重要的 能夠補充維生素
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 又開始說了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 嘴上沾到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.27,0:18:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反應等級上升到黃色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.64,0:18:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對象的監視等級也上升
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後稱其為BF509
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我想是上次的那個女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.21,0:18:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久遠大人似乎已經去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.05,0:18:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴雄 萬一出什麼事就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Larva反應還在上升
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WTOC部隊准備出動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解 WTOC部隊待命等級從4上升至3
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alpha到Epsilon開始裝載
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Larva反應還在上升
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超過監視等級也只是時間問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反應消失 沒有找到位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WTOC待機解除
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚了真是辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也讓它成為你的菜園裏的夥伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柿子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前跑進老家的倉庫裏 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現太爺的藤條箱裏有幾粒種子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.75,0:20:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到還真發芽了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你家庭院的那顆柿子樹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候還經常和你一起爬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都是你逼我爬的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是找借口把太爺抬出來 都跟你說我不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.23,0:20:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.58,0:20:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想保護她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.26,0:21:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺璃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老照顧我很無聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也出去外面玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.02,0:21:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偶爾也想一個人靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:21:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你回來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.26,0:22:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.00,0:22:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 請喝吧 綺璃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.37,0:22:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.39,0:22:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我來帶你參觀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.10,0:22:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是老板制定的方針
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.34,0:22:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的員工大部分都是像我們這樣年輕的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.37,0:22:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 百聞不如一見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.22,0:22:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩的開心點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.51,0:22:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮膚硬化嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.82,0:22:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次見到的能力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.82,0:22:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就是你的家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.97,0:22:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.82,0:23:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點啊 下一個要開始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.30,0:23:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.34,0:23:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 五個區域有各種各樣的娛樂設施
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.63,0:23:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2樓還有購物中心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.04,0:23:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊有吉祥物卷心菜君
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.40,0:23:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那邊等下去...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.50,0:23:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永久
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.78,0:23:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.75,0:23:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是首不錯的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.66,0:23:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫久遠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.23,0:23:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.25,0:24:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫綺璃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.88,0:24:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城崎綺璃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.12,0:24:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺璃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.64,0:24:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好聽的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.21,0:24:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺璃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.90,0:24:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.49,0:24:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定能夠再次說話 再次唱歌的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.06,0:25:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初要是沒生下你就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.36,0:25:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺璃的歌就像是天使的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.72,0:26:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 怎麼辦
