Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.42,0:26:26.46,shuoming,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ICU:重症加強護理病房
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.89,0:26:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
