Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.50,0:26:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.69,0:26:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.18,0:26:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 綺璃
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.10,0:27:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城崎女士
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.35,0:27:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現新的能量反應
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.78,0:27:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是昨晚丟失的BF509
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.66,0:27:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個反應也出現了 
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.01,0:27:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認是被「insania」帶走的BF503
