Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.17,0:28:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位准備展開
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.35,0:28:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接續完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.90,0:28:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀態一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.98,0:28:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alpha到Epsilon從BC開始分離
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.97,0:28:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2分鐘後進入普通道路
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.80,0:29:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界和平靠著秩序維持
