Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.09,0:29:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.24,0:29:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在封鎖道路
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.66,0:29:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那些鐵鏽人也...
