Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.04,0:29:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許會同時抓住他們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.07,0:29:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.14,0:29:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能同時救下兩個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.47,0:29:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久遠大人
