Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.19,0:32:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.72,0:32:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.39,0:32:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.53,0:32:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真頭疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.26,0:32:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒找到你 就要出大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.04,0:33:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由裏 剛才的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.10,0:33:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能說話了？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.43,0:33:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.22,0:33:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下再解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.52,0:33:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.80,0:33:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認是「insania」
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.03,0:33:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入第二階段
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.72,0:33:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.82,0:33:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.72,0:33:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由裏 
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.06,0:33:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由裏 聽到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.44,0:33:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由裏
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.45,0:33:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剃 我已經和綺璃匯合了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.07,0:33:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快讓久遠過來
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.92,0:33:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們就在裏面
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.08,0:33:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由普通檢索模式切換為熱能檢索模式
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.43,0:34:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.67,0:34:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到普通視覺模式 用肉眼直接尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.95,0:34:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.57,0:34:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 久遠快來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.04,0:34:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底是？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.90,0:34:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Attractor
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.38,0:34:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照神無月大叔的話說 就是覺醒者
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.22,0:34:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能將自己的思念變成力量的人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.69,0:34:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將思念化成力量
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.98,0:34:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷 怎麼突然變冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.55,0:34:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 而且你也是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.80,0:34:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.93,0:34:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.32,0:34:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別殺我
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.24,0:35:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內訌嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.07,0:35:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇馬 冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.48,0:35:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.05,0:35:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣 我也和你一樣有不完整的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.24,0:35:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此 我也想為拯救大家而使用這份力量
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.08,0:35:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的力量也一定能幫助大家
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.92,0:35:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰贏了呢 是「insania」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.80,0:35:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久遠大人...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.39,0:35:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 請不要再勉強自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.95,0:35:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.00,0:36:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久遠這笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.38,0:36:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點過來 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.22,0:36:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然會瞬間移動...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.70,0:36:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.20,0:36:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我要是先被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.16,0:36:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我死不瞑目的話
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.98,0:36:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫我把眼睛閉上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.51,0:37:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為啊 女生也很在意死相的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.07,0:37:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得沒那個空閑做這個
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.80,0:37:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.18,0:37:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丟失目標 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.76,0:37:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.22,0:37:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.67,0:38:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴雄
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.68,0:38:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.01,0:38:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.59,0:38:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你平時不好好鍛煉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.59,0:38:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.44,0:38:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺璃 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.45,0:38:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.36,0:38:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.13,0:38:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.74,0:38:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是..
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.58,0:38:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.38,0:38:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.61,0:39:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Delta 起作用了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.39,0:39:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 雖然勉強趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.80,0:39:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如情報所述 真是個難纏的家夥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.62,0:39:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 也到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.04,0:39:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.93,0:39:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.99,0:39:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工廠的安全系統被啟動了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.10,0:39:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰略部隊在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.43,0:39:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因還在調查中
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.87,0:39:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負責管轄那裏的警察以及消防隊很快會到達
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.82,0:39:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不是和日本政府對抗的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.89,0:39:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.00,0:40:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.98,0:40:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.90,0:40:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫柔點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.60,0:40:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.85,0:40:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒...沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.23,0:40:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.37,0:40:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明自己什麼都做不了 卻老愛說大話
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.40,0:40:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴雄
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.10,0:40:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.10,0:40:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只靠我一個人的力量是救不了大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.52,0:40:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你不是來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.45,0:40:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 貴雄
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.96,0:41:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有勇馬也是
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.30,0:41:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我破壞了約定
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.94,0:41:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這樣你才掌握了正確使用力量的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.10,0:41:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.02,0:41:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 還需要練習
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.55,0:41:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.69,0:41:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.28,0:41:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.40,0:41:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.08,0:41:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是我們的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.62,0:41:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管發生什麼 我都要保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.57,0:41:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護那些害怕自己能力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.41,0:41:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護像你和勇馬那樣不知所措的人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.60,0:41:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.91,0:41:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 我也需要大家的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.30,0:41:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也想借助你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.95,0:47:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為聽到了你痛苦的心聲
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.96,0:47:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秩序只能建立在犧牲之上
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.96,0:47:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鮮花和殺戮可不配啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.34,0:47:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能得救的有23人
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.08,0:47:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我 是久遠大人種的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.61,0:47:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們才沒有人類的感情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.86,0:47:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多人都被殺了 
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.26,0:47:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的犯人你也想救嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.87,0:47:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠之久遠 第二章
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.08,0:47:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混沌的蘭舞
